21:37.580 --> 21:39.340
I'm going to form my own house.

21:39.600 --> 21:43.059
It's my time, it's my dream,
and I'm going for it.

21:43.060 --> 21:45.090
I do not want any of your opinions.

21:45.190 --> 21:46.360
Not even mine?

21:46.460 --> 21:48.219
Honestly, no.

21:48.220 --> 21:50.220
But I do want your blessing.

21:50.660 --> 21:53.050
Believe me, this isn't
about you, it's about me.

21:53.130 --> 21:55.640
- What I need.
- That's for damn sure.

21:56.130 --> 21:59.170
Why would you want to leave my house?

21:59.270 --> 22:01.940
The house that found you and raised you?

22:02.040 --> 22:03.859
Because in our world,
there is only one way

22:03.860 --> 22:06.210
to leave something behind,
proof that I was here,

22:06.310 --> 22:09.500
building a legendary house
my way with my ideas.

22:09.600 --> 22:10.820
So that's it? You want a house

22:10.920 --> 22:14.199
so the world can sing your
glory for years to come?

22:14.200 --> 22:16.839
When I got kicked out, I
was a 17-year-old kid

22:16.840 --> 22:19.020
who didn't understand who I was,

22:19.120 --> 22:21.760
if I was gonna die in the
cold or from starvation.

22:21.840 --> 22:25.699
