give you that, but no more.

23:07.410 --> 23:09.580
Look at me. Look at you.

23:09.660 --> 23:10.980
I can pass.

23:11.020 --> 23:12.340
I can strut down Fifth Avenue

23:12.380 --> 23:14.210
when the sun is sitting
high as my cheekbones

23:14.310 --> 23:17.080
