23:30.360 --> 23:33.020
Or would you rather choke
on dust and decay?

23:33.040 --> 23:34.460
You'll be back.

23:37.540 --> 23:39.200
Never.

23:44.340 --> 23:46.140
Get your shady hands off of me.

23:46.860 --> 23:48.500
Justice.

24:02.330 --> 24:05.360
Hey, let go! Hey, let go!

24:06.160 --> 24:07.160
Hey!

24:09.800 --> 24:12.130
I told you, you got to
keep it on your back,

24:12.240 --> 24:14.320
