26:57.900 --> 27:00.299
So what exactly is a ball?

27:00.300 --> 27:01.979
Balls are a gathering of people

27:01.980 --> 27:04.360
who are not welcome to
gather anywhere else,

27:04.400 --> 27:06.470
a celebration of a life
that the rest of the world

27:06.570 --> 27:08.710
does not deem worthy of celebration.

27:08.810 --> 27:11.580
There are categories... people
dress up for them, walk.

27:11.680 --> 27:13.480
There's voting, trophies.

27:13.580 --> 27:14.826
Oh, can you, can you make money?

27:14.850 --> 27:16.410
Better than money.

27:16.520 --> 27:17.830
You can actually make
a name for yourself

27:17.850 --> 27:19.580
by winning a trophy or two.

27:19.690 --> 27:23.320
And in our community, the glory
of your name is everything.

27:23.420 --> 27:25.670
And we not gonna be walking the
red carpets at the Oscars,

27:25.690 --> 27:28.780
but this is our moment to become a star.

27:30.460 --> 27:32.730
Welcome to the ballroom world.

27:35.700 --> 27:38.700
