28:13.280 --> 28:16.760
The suit. The 401[K].

28:16.840 --> 28:18.720
The IRA.

28:18.740 --> 28:20.426
["LOVE'S THEME" BY THE LOVE
UNLIMITED ORCHESTRA PLAYING]

28:20.450 --> 28:21.650
Ah!

28:21.750 --> 28:24.620
