and sneak out to the balls.

29:58.380 --> 29:59.440
[BOTH LAUGH]

29:59.460 --> 30:00.880
Sneak back before they woke up.

30:00.980 --> 30:03.080
I thought I was so smart.

30:03.750 --> 30:05.880
Oh, then, on Thanksgiving...
I'll never forget...

30:05.990 --> 30:08.920
okay, my mother kept
looking and grinning,

30:09.020 --> 30:11.820
