are you grinning about?"

30:13.860 --> 30:14.890
[DAMON LAUGHS]

30:14.990 --> 30:16.480
You know what she said?

30:16.840 --> 30:19.660
She said, "Oh, you think you so clever.

30:19.770 --> 30:21.599
"I see that little young girl

30:21.600 --> 30:22.960
"who runs in and out of your room,

30:23.000 --> 30:26.070
