in the dark of the night."

30:26.170 --> 30:27.670
- I gagged.
- [LAUGHS]

30:27.770 --> 30:29.280
I was too stunned to speak.

30:29.640 --> 30:32.250
So she went on to say
how she wasn't mad,

30:32.260 --> 30:35.599
and she was just so relieved I
wasn't one of those sinful gays.

30:35.600 --> 30:36.780
Oh, my God, what did you do?

30:36.980 --> 30:39.120
I said, "Mother,

30:39.880 --> 30:42.950
"that was no strange woman
sneaking through your halls.

30:43.660 --> 30:45.020
"That was me.

30:45.120 --> 30:48.930
"I am not gay, and I am
certainly not sinful.

30:49.030 --> 30:52.130
"What I am is a woman, Mother.

30:53.100 --> 30:55.200
Not your son, but your daughter."

30:59.940 --> 31:01.840
[SIGHS]

31:01.940 --> 31:04.560
Well, she couldn't abide by that, no.

31:06.050 --> 31:08.720
She banished me from her
home and her heart.

31:10.850 --> 31:13.080
I cried like a baby.

31:13.540 --> 31:15.920
I left, and never looked back.

31:18.940 --> 31:21.399
When you get rejected by your mother,

31:21.400 --> 31:23.400
your father,

31:24.100 --> 31:27.520
you're always out there
looking for someone to...

31:27.820 --> 31:31.040
replace that love you're missing.

31:35.910 --> 31:37.940
Yeah... [CLEARS THROAT]

31:38.040 --> 31:40.280
Well, here, take my address.

31:41.760 --> 31:43.700
Come if you feel it's right for you.

31:43.920 --> 31:46.120
If nothing else...

31:47.840 --> 31:49.440
... tonight, you got an education.

31:52.130 --> 31:54.600
- Hmm.
- [BOTH LAUGH]

32:01.780 --> 32:03.980
- _
- [HORNS HONKING]

32:10.420 --> 32:12.390
[ELEVATOR CHIMES]

32:18.860 --> 32:20.760
MATT: <i>"Stan Bowes."</i>

32:20.870 --> 32:22.830
"Bowes," what kind of,
what kind of name is that?

32:22.930 --> 32:24.530
We're Irish-Italian.

32:25.440 --> 32:27.440
What's your background?

32:27.540 --> 32:29.300
I was born in Rye, then
Riverdale, Princeton,

32:29.320 --> 32:30.840
Wharton MBA, just like the boss.

32:30.940 --> 32:33.076
