32:35.900 --> 32:37.200
You're from New Jersey.

32:37.240 --> 32:38.680
Usually, that's a detriment.

32:38.780 --> 32:40.766
[CHUCKLING]: Yeah, not here.
I'm the unicorn in this place.

32:40.790 --> 32:42.180
Trump is from Queens. He likes people

32:42.190 --> 32:43.600
who speak the same language as him.

32:43.620 --> 32:45.000
Know how to get things done.

32:45.120 --> 32:46.996
I ask everyone who comes in
here looking for a job...

32:47.020 --> 32:49.180
right down to the janitor...
what do you want?

32:49.860 --> 32:53.120
Not money-wise, what do you want?

32:54.500 --> 32:55.700
[EXHALES]

32:55.800 --> 32:57.430
Well, I want to be you.

32:57.540 --> 32:59.440
[TITTERS]

32:59.540 --> 33:00.800
That's a very good answer.

33:00.910 --> 33:02.810
I want what you have.

33:03.080 --> 33:05.540
