my wife, and just go buy it.

33:10.780 --> 33:13.080
The new American Dream.

33:13.520 --> 33:15.280
For the first time in American history,

33:15.300 --> 33:17.740
it's considered a good thing
to flaunt your success, right?

33:17.880 --> 33:19.590
Let people know how rich you are.

33:19.690 --> 33:20.790
This watch?

33:20.890 --> 33:23.080
Patek Philippe, rose gold, nine grand.

33:23.090 --> 33:24.340
